story, policy, education studies, and philosophy, as well as to policy-makers, educational administrators and teachers"--cProvided by publisher.  a4110aWhite, John,d1934 November 7- 0aEducationxPhilosophy. 0aMoral education.1 aSuissa, Judith,d1966-eeditor of compilation.1 aWinstanley, Carrie,eeditor of compilation.1 aMarples, Roger,eeditor of compilation. 0aRoutledge research in education ;v122.  aLB 880 W482 E38 2015c1hUAED-Bi0162035232212  aLB 880 W482 E38 2015wLCc1i0162035232212d1/17/2017e1/10/2017lFLOOR_2mUAEDUCn3p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/4/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n98089249bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/27239387